    • Order

      public Order(String streetAddress, String city, String state, String zip, String name, String item, String category)
      Constructor for the order class. Initializes order with address information, name of person who ordered, and item and category of the order
      Parameters:
      streetAddress - street address of order
      city - city address of order
      state - state address of order
      zip - zipcode section of address of order
      name - name of person creating order
      item - item that is being "ordered"
      category - category the item is part of
